text: Natalia Guadalupe Brussa (born 13 February 1985) is an Argentine volleyball player. She played at the 2002 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. She played for Scavolini Pesaro, Universal Modena, and Tauron MKS Dabrowa Gornicza. == References == Category:Argentine volleyball players Category:Living people Category:1985 births
